name: Acid dreams
description:
We open up wonderful paths to pursue goals and develop skill in our work. And as soon as we seriously take on a task worth mastering it to perfection, many new paths open before us, and creative conviction gives us purity and happiness. And then our life becomes richer and more meaningful.
 Quote by Marilyn W. Atkinson

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2019, spray paint on canvas, 90x90cm. 8438x8374 pix
